  <h3>Construction</h3>
    <p>The Batteries will be placed underneath solar panel structure. A micro controller will control when the batteries are charge or not to prevent over charging.</p>
    <p>Our system runs at 12V. Using the Trojan T-105 6V lead acid battery, we will put two batteries in series. Any increase in power storage will be handled by connecting a pair of batteries in series, in parallel with each other. </p>

